0Z","msg":"Flashforward 應該唔太出名 但係覺得劇情幾緊湊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ah2GD5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ah2GD5.jpg&h=c5c3663a&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T18:54:31.000Z","msg":"打開佐我美劇大門"},{"pid":"c19432fa97b77bc2f0f2dc090c5332b6f288913a","tid":2476744,"uid":252854,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T18:59:02.000Z","msg":"Person of Interest<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />知佢完 但好想佢拍落去<br />\n另外有套Ioan Gruffudd做嘅叫Forever 覺得題材好得意 但冇續到下一季好想睇埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51f203db7e57d52a7257402e591c313084decc1a","tid":2476744,"uid":148245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T19:23:57.000Z","msg":"orphan black!!<br />\n雖然已經五季，ending完得幾好，無乜空間再作落去，但真係好掛住每個角色<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVquYKHpaw9mDguohzefUh3T8in1v8cvmVYSkH1u2GdK7?filename=w2DM8JX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw2DM8JX.jpg&h=25db8e78&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f350e5247a2558b0ece93946a575037b83600a64","tid":2476744,"uid":8198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T19:29:51.000Z","msg":"lie to me"},{"pid":"7ef5d09f8645e2d05d8d751045bae3ba4f803a4f","tid":2476744,"uid":371001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T19:30:02.000Z","msg":"Z Nation<br />\nBreaking Bad<br />\nGotham<br />\nDay Break<br />\nReality Z"},{"pid":"bf7cf5bf8a2cad87110f96601a26be32e810629c","tid":2476744,"uid":305085,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T19:40:35.000Z","msg":"Dirk gently's holistic detective agency"},{"pid":"093b966359ceae76d1692ab297b23b8409e250a7","tid":2476744,"uid":396347,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8f08e10290b2e6b72baabf2acb0a78b60069d407","tid":2476744,"uid":268275,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T18:46:55.000Z","msg":"Sense 8 <br />\n<br />\n中文好似叫咩超感8人組<br />\n<br />\n果陣睇完第二季知佢無筆直比人cut左第三季sad到爆，到最後有返個2小時結尾叫好dd。<br />\n<br />\n真心覺得呢套好L正，d鏡頭，音樂，sex嘅場面好L靚 <br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇巴絲同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都想揾d類似呢套睇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T19:51:48.000Z","msg":"其實個故事idea都好正<br />\n科幻得黎講感情D位都好睇 無論係關於愛情友情親情<br />\n最鐘意睇印度妹Kala同德國佬Wolfie條線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nS2好似啱啱將個劇情拓展開去, 之後就因為budget問題比Netflix cancel左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(不過套劇真係去好多國家實景拍攝,冰島德國非洲英國韓國印度西班牙美國,係真係好重皮)<br />\n有生之年都唔知有無機會睇之後幾季<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我覺得呢套劇個故仔加埋拍攝手法好unique(科幻劇入面又會探討性別,身份認同,宗教呢D議題), 暫時都未搵到有一套似佢(而且都無咩其他劇會有咁多budget去唔同國家拍嘢, 套劇嘅導演同編劇仲要係拍The Matrix嘅Wachowskis姊妹, 佢地本身都擅長呢類科幻題材,又有份構思呢個咁特別嘅故事)"},{"pid":"cd7a6467d37ec0d642aa6462f5aaf11644a5ac9d","tid":2476744,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6aea4a928062164fad2a1772e9db42fa524598eb","tid":2476744,"uid":49426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T18:19:35.000Z","msg":"Person of Interest"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T20:10:40.000Z","msg":"有完整結局"},{"pid":"b1af478c94550d59f77fc303380f11469d2777a0","tid":2476744,"uid":220416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T20:14:15.000Z","msg":"下black mirror唔拍啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好期待第六季<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973d62c038847a548c5eba9073777d3a3279ad19","tid":2476744,"uid":293368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02401777711903bdd51b48f1d902dc93741b449e","tid":2476744,"uid":142320,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T17:48:57.000Z","msg":"The Society"},"citedBy":0,"r