slike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ca1bac39447a765656008e0dc060488b287a1d2","tid":2476744,"uid":81756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T18:44:06.000Z","msg":"freskish<br />\nsalvation <br />\nstalker<br />\nzombieland<br />\nsanta clarita diet"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T23:42:22.000Z","msg":"Santa Clarita Diet 好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔太長一隻 又好笑 兩公婆又sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74710bb7db8d97eb9872b9b7b71f358ffe5a4c58","tid":2476744,"uid":185469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T23:56:38.000Z","msg":"英劇Utopia<br />\n烏托邦實驗是一本神秘的傳奇繪圖小說，但是一群之前從無任何聯繫的人卻發現自己擁有了這本小說的原稿，於是他們的生活突然因此一團亂， 他們不斷遭受神秘殺手組織'The Network'的追殺，於是這群受驚的人群如果想要存活，只有唯一一條路：那就是逃亡。<br />\n<br />\n當年睇完呢段youtube即刻比佢d拍攝手法，配樂同畫面吸引！成套劇d畫面都拍得好靚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />美國版聽講唔好睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mOeeFajZtE4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmOeeFajZtE4&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=ebbd1cb9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mOeeFajZtE4</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYVtZCGQYgj4g2utexRa5zfFdJ64fMxxiNY9NcikgYqTy?filename=hVFS5KN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhVFS5KN.jpg&h=935d6027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英劇In the Flesh<br />\n在喪屍大爆發之後。這次喪屍爆發在劇中被稱作「復生」（The Rising），而劇情就發生在復生之後。劇情主要描述的是主角，少年Kieren Walker從喪屍狀態復活之後重新融入當地人類社會的過程。<br />\n<br />\n好特別既題材，又有感人同估唔到既位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cxibk4zwqdY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fcxibk4zwqdY&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLTBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=5acdcf0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cxibk4zwqdY</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ9j3cJBKRMParTWrnSkneDrL5XXGuLsejDmMHemUwyKv?filename=OMvf3wV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOMvf3wV.jpg&h=4f6b1303&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76df556a9903db4a513d5d33d4af50184be0ec46","tid":2476744,"uid":20641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://miro.medium.com/max/1000/1*qouImYc54ZYqhiRsGegzdQ@2x.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmiro.medium.com%2Fmax%2F1000%2F1%2AqouImYc54ZYqhiRsGegzdQ%402x.jpeg&h=6b112dd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"08e9e18c2a03dbaeeb6a6dd8d0aafeb5338fa8e8","tid":2476744,"uid":364767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T00:33:30.000Z","msg":"Seinfeld"},{"pid":"72d4f56171ffcd8a463eb0062d8f93fce760892a","tid":2476744,"uid":369558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T00:37:52.000Z","msg":"stranger things"},{"pid":"1f4412403ed6ad85cadb9d30a6c142d6bd0e4f69","tid":2476744,"uid":344857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T00:41:36.000Z","msg":"sense8<br />\ndesperate housewife"},{"pid":"d95a0b83f52aeec91adcfdc68b5c553d25f22610","tid":2476744,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T00:43:12.000Z","msg":"想知醫神house係完左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個睇到第五定六季就無睇 好似係<br />\n記得好似同左院長一齊又分左手？"},{"pid":"582ddbad9f64d4cd2273448e7b0258843b2bf63d","tid":2476744,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d95a0b83f52aeec91adcfdc68b5c553d25f22610","tid":2476744,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T00:43:12.000Z","msg":"想知醫神house係完左定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個睇到第五定六季就無睇 好似係<br />\n記得好似同左院長一齊又分左手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T01:12:13.000Z","msg":"完左，最後一季女院長因為要求加人工結果被踢走，所以無佢份"},{"pid":"a253dbea06765b345c53a01a07ad37e1bb8c4207","tid":2476744,"uid":188482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score